Brand Identity Overview: Skyliqua
Industry: Premium Water Purification Systems
Core Aesthetic: Luxury, Fluidity, Purity, and Professionalism.

1. Visual Assets & Logo
Logo Composition: A combination mark featuring a stylized, metallic-finish cloud icon above three flowing wave lines. The wordmark "skyliqua" is positioned below, with the tagline "water purifiers" encased in a thin horizontal frame.

Icon Details: High-shine, 3D chrome/silver finish on the clouds and waves, suggesting cleanliness and high-tech filtration.

Graphic Pattern: A marble-style fluid art background using a mix of deep teal, seafoam green, and veins of metallic gold.

2. Typography
Primary Font (Headings): Playfair Display (Bold). A sophisticated serif that conveys elegance and authority.

Secondary Font (Body/Subheadings): Montserrat. A clean, modern geometric sans-serif for readability and a contemporary feel.

3. Color Palette (Hex Codes)
Deep Forest Teal: #22615F (Primary Brand Color)

Ocean Teal: #22615F (Secondary / Accent)

Pale Sage: #A5CBC1 (Soft Neutral)

Muted Bronze: #AC885B (Metallic/Luxury Accent)

Dusty Gold: #A9956B (Secondary Metallic)

Sand Gold: #E1C06D (Highlight Metallic)

4. Design Elements & Applications
Imagery Style: Use of "glassy" finishes, realistic mockups (water purifiers with metallic accents), and high-contrast lighting.

Apparel: Black polo shirts with the full-color logo on the left chest for the "Professional Installation Team."

Marketing Tagline: "THE CLOUD OF PURE WATER."

Layout: Minimalist with generous white space, thin gold borders, and structured hierarchy.